task.summary: Default task
Small cleanup with no major changes.
Small cleanup with no major changes.

Large content push.
Prototype directional sprites with pipeline for rendering models as spritesheets. Currently the snail model is used with actual depth and normal maps.
Updated the name of some flec components to become more standardized.
Project cleanup. Removed old testing files and moved many folders around.
More verbose building. Block build extra if already running. Added faster building and cache but on empty builds did not help in a meaningful way.
Continued project cleanup. Added stone textures.
Added scon cache folders to gitignore. Updated workspace xml file.
Ignored a number of files to make clion a bit faster.

Fixed bug with death animations, where death counter was not incremented each frame after being reset to 0 at beginning of frame.
Added flec life change debug component.
Spawning prefabs now provides more information on components. Added new folders for directional sprites.

Fixed bug with death animations, where death counter was not incremented each frame after being reset to 0 at beginning of frame.
Added flec life change debug component.
Spawning prefabs now provides more information on components. Added new folders for directional sprites.

Directional renderers no longer need to set where they find color/normal maps and instead use config or local search.
Added component for spawning entities based on distance traveled.

Added detailed rotation, which rotates the plane slightly to create smooth rotations. In a good state.
Preparing to simplify UI for flec.

Final changes to entities.
Preparing to simplify UI for flec.
Changed name of groups to Flec Components to make it more clear.
Replacing UI components with prefab instanced ones.
Added method to add components for flecs. this allows correct debug printouts.
Added some rendering information.
Removed directional sprite rendering as a choice. Now always available in prefabs.

Continued refactors. Grouping common setups together for prefabs. Removing now unused data components that are now implemented on prefab.
replaced old method of setting up flec component list with modern version. yay!
Added new flec xp orb with sounds.
Fixed memory leak where each frame a new query was created but never deleted.
Added item contributions, xp orbs to enemy prefab type.
Fire projectiles now work. Added static explosion for fire.
Added back red flashing damage.
Removed temp files.
Removing art assets so they can be added to git ignore.
Adding leftover changes.
Split position into two different components.
Added more advanced rotation update system. Added `FPositionVelocity` to store last frames position changes.
Added enitty on spawn random offset for position and angle after it has spawned.
Run renderer in parallel.
Added X, Y debug labels to scene view. This is not rendered.

Large refactor with rotations. We had a mix between different rotations and methods to get angle between them leading to bugs.
Reversed render directions in renderer.

Large refactor with rotations. We had a mix between different rotations and methods to get angle between them leading to bugs.
Reversed render directions in renderer.
Ignore optional render output folder.
Modified the spawn function for a simpler interface. Now checks if spawning on floor as an optioanl argument.
Added item modifiers which add an onhit ability activator. Modified abilities to support on hit activation.
Cleaned up unused entity.

Replaced AbilityItemNodeDescriptor with AbilityDescriptor which acts more like a generator class to simplify nodes. Fixed issue where abilities were not connecting to resource pools. Made invisible abilities not visible in the view.
NOTE - Abilities do not spawn entities.
Fixed issue where onhit spawns would crash due to not suspending defer. Added warning Removed emitters - abilities are now spawned as direct flecs.
Fixed issue where onhit spawns would crash due to not suspending defer. Added warning Removed emitters - abilities are now spawned as direct flecs.
Completed refactor of player abilities and how they connect. New system has less hardcoded details at odd levels. UI elements are now optional.
Fixed issue where ability textures were not updating in UI.
Cleaned up resource UI to a single reuseable type for both mana and stamina.
Added type to error when godot finds a class which does not exist. Happens usually when refactoring.
Removed spawned projectiles when unequipping an item. This is to avoid projectiles having references to now cleared abilities.
Separated on hit and onkill modifiers. Added more descriptive context for damage. This is really poorly done and needs ripping out when I replace damage/spawning system with a simpler pattern.
Removed unused flecs world. Added additional logging to flecs. Enabled flecs explorer support.
Diabling test to build.
Diabling test to build.
